revisions.description: Added hostname, alarm/warning count, and manufacturer to deviceInfo

Removed current min, max, and peak fields from pdu phase, line, breaker, and outlet tables Removed voltage min, max, and peak fields from pdu phase, line, breaker, and outlet tables Removed minmax reset value from pduOutletMeterReset Added balance field to pdu phase table
Modified pduOutletSwitchTable to support outlet actions with delays
Changed SYNTAX of objects, with a UTF-8 encoded string value, to SnmpAdminString

Added pduBreakerCurrentPeak, pduLineCurrentPeak, pduOutletMeterCurrentPeak, pduPhaseVoltagePeak, and pduPhaseCurrentPeak Updated object descriptions, indicating which fields are not supported on all platforms
Added trapObj group with trap payload objects Added additional payload objects to trap definitions
Added productPlatform to deviceInfo group Added product identity entries
